[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14516] changed tests which may invoke externals to use non-conflicting names
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14495] made 
``glob``
 stream
Bahex 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14446] refactored 
``term query``
 and added a 
``--prefix``
 flag
, and added a 
``path self``
 command for getting absolute paths to files at parse time (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14303] 1
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14538] 2
)
fdncred 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14524] added file column to 
``scope modules``
 output
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14492] allowed 
``select``
 to stream more
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14486] added environment variables for sourced files
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14390] added function to make env vars case-insensitive
amtoine 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14519] fixed multiline strings in NDNUON
ratherforky 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14510] fixed a silent failure in command signature parsing
michel-slm 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14502] bumped the 
``titlecase``
 dependency
alex-kattathra-johnson 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14494] shortened --max-time in tests and used a more stable error check
IanManske 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14485] added 
``--long``
 flag for 
``sys cpu``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14484] removed duplicate implementations of 
``CallExt::rest``
RobbingDaHood 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14481] fixed file path completion for custom commands
PegasusPlusUS 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14411] added feature: PWD-per-drive to facilitate working on multiple drives on Windows
Jasha10 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14358] enabled 
``test_cp_recurse``
 on macOS
sgvictorino 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14353] normalized special characters in module names to allow variable access
musicinmybrain updated dependencies (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14513] 1
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14489] 2
)
sholderbach 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14520] improved the 
``sleep``
 example using multiple durations
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14493] added 
``remove``
 as a search term on 
``drop``
 commands
ayax79 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14527] improved documentation and error handling around 
``polars with-column --name``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14491] converted Filesize to Int for 
``polars``
cptpiepmatz 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14488] fixed the missing 
``installed_plugins``
 field in 
``version``
maxim-uvarov 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14533] tweaked error message wording
